WEBVTT

13:24.691 --> 13:26.024
Oh! The distributors!

13:26.024 --> 13:27.441
-They'll take money from anyone!
-Enough, enough.

13:27.441 --> 13:28.274
I won't allow it, Georgekutty.

13:28.274 --> 13:30.149
Sir, can't we give them
just two shows?

13:30.149 --> 13:31.191
Not possible!

13:31.524 --> 13:33.149
Don't be so rigid, sir.

13:33.233 --> 13:34.483
I'm not being rigid.

13:34.524 --> 13:35.858
Come on, please cooperate!
